9-12-04T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"報老廉唔可以同人講"},{"pid":"059bb5ef37259e7d44a482ce2930d21918724c88","tid":1768642,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6Oi3Go.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6Oi3Go.gif&h=182b5963&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ebe2d7273d0b9ec74901e513d5c2fb639a294b5","tid":1768642,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"廉政公署通警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f45f4a3df18f42f6c9bda3971488c7a784ecf7","tid":1768642,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"睇到有d迷迷地<br />\n不過我知道要支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}